      This fits your .

    • 6-Port Massive Expansion USB C Hub: UGREEN 6-in-1 USB-C data hub splitter features a 4K HDMI output port, SD and TF card readers, 2 USB 3.0 ports and 100W power delivery charging port(Max. 20V 5A ). And all hub ports can work simultaneously, small yet mighty. Compatible with MacBook Pro 2019/2018/2017/2016 13” 15”, Samsung Galaxy S10/S9/S9 Plus/S8/S8 Plus/Note 10 9 8, Dell XPS 15 13, Huawei P30/P30 Pro​/P20/P20 Pro​/Mate 10 Pro/Mate 20/Mate 20 Pro, Surface Go/Book 2
    • 4K HDMI Razor-sharp Resolution: Mirror or extend your screen with UGREEN USB C adapter HDMI port and directly stream 4K UHD (3840x2160@30Hz), Full HD 1080p or 3D video to HDTV, monitor or projector. You could enjoy movies with your family on a bigger screen, or making a vivid presenting in a meeting.
    • 5Gbps Superspeed Data Transfer: Sync files directly among the storage devices, like hard drive and SD card. This USB Type C hub adds extra 2 USB 3.0 ports for connecting USB peripheral devices such as flash drive, hard drive, keyboard, mouse, MP3 player etc with 5Gbps max, transferring HD videos in seconds. Support SD and TF cards reading simultaneously with the highest speed up to 100MB/S.
    • 100W USB C Power Delivery: Type-C female input on this USB C OTG hub dock allows you to charge the newest MacBook Pro, Dell XPS, or other Type-C laptops at max 100W (20V/5A, 15V/3A, 9V/3A, 5V/3A), even while connecting multiple peripherals for data transferring. USB C female port support PD charging only, not for data transmission. PD charging adapter is sold separately.
    • Compact Size & Mac-style: Compact and lightweight, allows you to expand your laptops'capabilities while on-the-go. UGREEN USB-C hub with a sleek aluminum finish perfectly blend in with MacBook. The aluminum case is better for heat dissipation, electronic component and circuitry will be conducted to outside more quickly, making this USB C adapter safer to use.

    Product Description

    Most Efficient Workstation Gadget

    UGREEN USB C multiport adapter gives you all the ports you need for work or home life. Connect a host of devices, including external hard drives, keyboard and flash drives, to maximize efficiency. SD TF Card Reader allows you to take photos off your DSLR and edit them on the phone. And a 4K HDMI port and a power port let you connect your fast charging PD power adaptor to keep you in charge.

    Universal Compatibility

    USB Type C PC/Tablet

    Apple: MacBook 2018/2017/2016/2015, Macbook Pro 2019/2018/2017/2016 13" 15", MacBook Air 2019/2018, iMac 2019/2017, iMac Pro 2019, Mac mini 2018, New MacBook with Thunderbolt 3, iPad Pro 2020/2019/2018 with IOS 13.0 and above (Ensure the file format of usb external storage device is EXFAT or FAT32. )

    Samsung: Galaxy Tab S4/S5e/S6, Chromebook Pro/Plus, Galaxy Book 12"/10.6"/Tab Pro S 12"

    ASUS: Chromebook Flip, ZenBook3, ASUS ZenBook Pro, Asus ZenBook Flip, ASUS Transformer 3 Pro T303UA

    HP: EliteBook 840 G1/840 G3/Folio G1, Spectre X360/Spectre 13, ENVY 13/X360

    Lenovo: Legion Y530/Y740, ThinkPad X1 Carbon (6th Gen/5th Gen)/X1 Carbon extreme, ThinkPad T480s/T480, Yoga 920/910, Ideapad Air 12, Miix 630

    DELL: XPS 13/15/12 9250, Inspiron 13 15 7000/5000, Precision 5510, Latitude 7285, Acer: swift 7, Acer Chromebook, Xiaomi: Mi Notebook Air 12.5/13.3, Mi Notebook Pro 15.6 "

    100W Type-C Power Delivery Charging

    The type-c hub supports a high-level of charging up to 100W. The hub itself only consumes 8W even when fully loaded so no need to worry about losing power.

    4K UHD Visual Feast

    HDMI output supports video resolutions up to 4K@30Hz UHD or 1080P@60Hz to an external screen. Connect your usb-c smart phone or iPad Pro to showcase your content in a bigger, better way.

    Fast SD TF Card

    USB C card reader easily expands SD/TF slot and reads and writes 2 cards at the same time to keep you away from the hassle of constant unplugging and re-plugging.

    SD Slot: Support UHS-I (SD, SDXC, SDHC, RS-MMC)

    TF Slot: Support UHS-I (Micro SD, Micro SDHC, Micro SDXC)

    Read more

    True USB 3.0 Ports

    This USB Type C hub adds extra 3 USB 3.0 ports for your laptop, allowing to connect multiple USB peripherals. Support faster data transfer up to 5Gbps, 10X faster than USB 2.0.

    Built-in chip

    The intelligent temperature control chip could assure a stable working condition. EMI protection to prevent interfere with wireless devices.

    Compact Size

    Designed 4.5*1.4*0.5 inch, with a sleek aluminum-alloy housing in a gunmetal finish, easy to set into your laptop sleeve or bag.

        5.0 out of 5 stars Charges my Pixel 3a XL
        Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2019
        Verified Purchase
        I got this because I needed a USB hub that also charges my phone while I'm using it. I can confirm that it does exactly that. I don't have to plug anything in an any particular order (like micro ubs ones of the past). I can plug the hub in, and then the power cord, or have the hub powered and plug it into the phone, either way it charges at over 1A (1.3 to 1.5A is typical). My tester has standard USB connections, so on a rapid USB-C to USB-C charger it may actually go beyond that level.

        I have not tried the HDMI display, but it does throw a warning on my windows 10 laptop when I plug it in that the display may be limited. That's fine, I just got it to use on my cell phone for connecting USB ports, the HDMI is more of a bonus.

        Very pleased with this purchase. Will buy more uGreen products (Already have some cables in my cart as we speak). I look forward to trying more of their accessories.
